There could be three possibilty

1) The length of the given array is less than 2*k +1 ie,no   circle formed by given arra.
    solution:In this case we just have to store the as many -1 as there in the given array in the answer vector and return.

2) The length of the given vector is zero.
    solution:just return the given vector

3) The length of the vector is greater than 2k+1 i,e circles are possible of radius k
    solution: just store k times -1 for the numbers having left radius less than k.
then run a loop to store the sum of numbers whose radius is k.
again store k times -1 for the numbers whose right radius is less than k.
NOTE:take sum as double not int as the sum of 2k+1 can exceeds the range of int.
